CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: CleanSpark (Nasdaq: CLSK), America's Bitcoin Miner, is a market-leading, pure play bitcoin miner with a proven track record of success. We own and operate a portfolio of mining facilities across the United States powered by globally competitive energy prices. Sitting at the intersection of Bitcoin, energy, operational excellence and capital stewardship, we optimize our mining facilities to deliver superior returns to our shareholders. Monetizing low-cost, high reliability energy by securing the most important finite, global asset - Bitcoin - positions us to prosper in an ever-changing world.
